      "description": "Patch 2.1.42.1149.1 (Eudora's Revamped, 2026)\n\nA jungle build for the Prince of the Abyss that focuses on sustain fights.\n\nContext of the order of the Build:\n1. Swap for Warrior Boots if the enemy has many Physical Heroes, otherwise use Tough Boots for Crowd Control (CC) Reduction.\n\n2. War Axe for the sustain and spell vamp stats.\n\n3. Dominance Ice for hybrid defense, useful for team fights.\n\n4. Radiant Armor against mage that deals \"continuous\" damage, swap for Athena Shield when fighting against a \"burst\" mage, otherwise just use Radiant Armor.\n\n5. Queen Wings for the spell vamp stats and damage reduction, swap for Immortality or Winter Truncheon for second life, though Queen Wings is more preferable in terms of sustainability.\n\n6. Chastise Pauldron against attack speed heroes mainly for Marksmen, swap for Antique Cuirass if the enemy has many strong Physical Skill Caster.",
